description._content: Description: View of a few seed bearers of Aleppo Pine, left after War Felling of 1918 - 1920. Diorios Forest, Elevation 750 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Description: View of Kioni Forest Hut (On the right ) in 1922. Makhera Forest, Elevation 4,000 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
